<item>
            <title>[LU-2710] Remove function resolution mistakes made by Coverity</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2710</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Coverity tool found some false out-of-bound access errors in the Lustre code. These false positives are due to bad function resolutions made by Coverity. The verification of such mistakes takes quite a long time.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Following what was previously done in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1907&quot; title=&quot;Remove function resolution mistakes made by Coverity&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1907&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1907&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, I will propose a new patch to address new occurrences of those false positives.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
